Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:05.77,comntry,,0,0,0,,WARNING: this commentary contains spoilers. Watch after completing the series.\NAlso, commentary tracks are not held to the same translation standard as regular dialogue tracks. This is a rough TL.\N{\1c&H548DFF&}The guest this time is the Cheif Animation Director: \N{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs50}谷口淳一郎{\fn\fs} (Taniguchi Jun'ichirou).
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:03.48,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Okay! Um, so then, we are continuing, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:10.44,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Episode 8 {\i1}I'm Really An Idiot{\i0} um... commentary, with the role of Madoka, I am Yuuki Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:08.61,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.32,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yup, and with the role of Homura, I'm Saitou Chiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:14.07,chiwa,,0,0,0,,And, this time's guest—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.03,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,And!{\alpha&HFF&}ahis time's guest—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:14.03,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}And, this time'{\alpha} guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:16.32,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ah, Chief Animation Director, I'm Taniguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:17.37,taniguti,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:18.83,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:18.83,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.12,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Wow, you deal with the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:21.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This unsettling atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.08,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.25,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:23.83,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Reall—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:30.30,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Well, for starters, the amazing visuals sort of distracted me... um,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:28.46,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}Well, for starters, the {\alpha}amazing visuals{\alpha&HFF&} sort of distracted me... um,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:29.63,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,ga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:35.18,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Chief Animation Director Taniguchi-san is someone I'd like to talk to now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.05,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:38.51,chiwa,,0,0,0,,For starters... what sort of feeling does the work you do have?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:38.51,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,What sort of work is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:44.81,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Um, as an official description, it's making sure the series and characters hold unity overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:40.47,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:45.44,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:45.98,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.65,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't really come out though (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:49.98,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aeee{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:49.98,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uuuu{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:49.98,taniguti,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:55.57,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So you go to each individual animator-san, and sort of iron out the wrinkles?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:55.57,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's right. Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:55.57,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:57.24,chiwa,,0,0,0,,For the characters, ensuring the entire time that they are—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.95,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seeing the series overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:58.53,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.74,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,What an amazing sense of balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:00.74,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.29,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:03.00,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's quite difficult, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.16,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Right–Well, actually, that isn't particularly true, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:10.59,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Really, it's the people who draw the original images and who actually draw the movements that have it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:09.25,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:11.17,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:17.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So, you look it all over, and say "fix this part up a little bit" to grab hold of a balance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:14.51,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:17.68,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Right. That's right. Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:19.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huaaaa{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:22.93,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,By the way, about how many people are there drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:28.90,taniguti,,0,0,0,,About... There are around 10 people who create the original pictures and movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.36,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:30.36,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:37.36,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Then, as for people who make corrections... there are about one or two of those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:34.44,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:44.87,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Then, there's me as well, who also deals with the drawing of pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:41.45,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:43.75,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.75,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Then, there's a feeling of fixing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.37,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hee{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.08,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heeeee{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:50.13,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:50.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:50.67,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,So it's like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:53.63,chiwa,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people collaborating for that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:53.38,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne~?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.55,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But it's truly amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.55,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:02:05.18,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's especially true for the work this time. The battle scenes, and the transformation scenes too, they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.14,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:04.43,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:12.11,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol) They have so much movement, and the angles and such have a somewhat unique feeling, it's kind of like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.65,chiwa,,0,0,0,,In normal — Well, somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:19.20,chiwa,,0,0,0,,compared to normal {\i1}mahou shoujo{\i0} shows, the fighting style is yet another very different thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.12,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ba– They really have a "{\i1}shounen{\i0} battle" resemblance to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.12,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Right. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:26.75,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Is there any discrepancy in that viewpoint to you, in regards to the writing style?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.25,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Writing style...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:32.59,taniguti,,0,0,0,,No, um, for us too, when we see the content, we're surprised each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.05,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Like "What's this!?" (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.00,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:36.55,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.93,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, then, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:44.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The scenes with movement and stillness have a large contrast... Isn't that quite intense?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:40.72,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:49.81,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really, we've talked about this previously, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:56.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Scenes where just two people talk while sitting down, scenes where they talk through their facial expressions...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:51.85,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:52.94,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:56.36,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.44,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Madoka{\fnArial Unicode MS}☆{\fn}Magika{\i0} has quite a few of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.44,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,They're there, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.11,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:04.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, we were very cautious about that point when acting out those scenes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:02.45,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:10.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Drawing facial expressions... somehow... "How do you decide on those?" was something we thought about a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.29,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:15.13,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then on air—Ah, well after knowing what it is on air it's a bit like "That", but for me—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.75,taniguti,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:14.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,ahahaha~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:20.13,chiwa,,0,0,0,,During the after recording, there were still many facial expressions I still didn't know, and when we saw them on air...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:25.43,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's true for Madoka right here too, but it's like "So it's this kind of face" or "Here you can't see her eyes."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:22.30,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:28.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Um, that is, a facial expression where you can't see their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.27,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.22,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.85,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, "Here was a close-up on the eyes?" or such.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:32.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,We came to know that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:32.56,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.73,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Do you help with achieving balance in that sort of area, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:39.65,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's right, primarily in deciding the art for facial expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.32,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:43.57,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Really, when it comes time to draw, I'll try the facial expressions and such myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.87,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:44.57,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:49.33,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pr–probably, um, to other people it looks like I'm making some disgusting faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.58,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Making those faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:49.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:49.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.87,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Doing similar facial expressions would be pretty unpleasant (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.88,taniguti,,0,0,0,,I was making sad faces. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:53.88,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:04:00.80,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Having done that, when I saw them done properly on screen, I was quite happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:01.97,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heee{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:01.72,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:08.22,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Then, what is it... this atmosphere the art holds, since it's Ume-sensei, the character's faces are wide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.48,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.48,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,They have quite a sorrowful feeling to them, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.02,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Especially since they're wide, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.02,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne? Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:19.19,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, when I see that kind of expression I think "Eh, amazing!" everytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:25.95,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ah, in the beginning really, um... these characters made some {\i1}kyun{\i0}-style smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.70,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:32.62,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Halfway through, that stops. Um... really, the conversations become quite heavy, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.54,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:36.33,taniguti,,0,0,0,,It results in absolutely no smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.54,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:46.22,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Somehow, at the very beginning of the opening, when you really want to hug Madoka, that distressful crying face...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.10,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It isn't really... what is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:55.06,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,The animation is quite... seeing it in just a "4-pattern" style, I wouldn't have thought it was so moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:05:01.82,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I think the art is amazing. I really love that face. Somehow... I feel thankful for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:02.86,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:11.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,When we did our acting, we put a considerable amount of feeling into it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:19.13,chiwa,,0,0,0,,When we did that, like when you heard our acting, did that give you a hand later on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.30,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ah, that is, um... um, it was instructional, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:26.76,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Well, when we drew most of the art, after recording was finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:26.76,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.63,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.26,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.26,taniguti,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.26,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.26,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Well, you persevered to make the art!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.26,taniguti,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:30.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:31.39,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.77,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But even still, to think it moves this much... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.39,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,So difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:41.69,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really, this time there are so many scenes like this one, which successfully portray "true feelings."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:40.44,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:47.66,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It hurt so much, and there was no helping it when we were acting it out, but for the people drawing the art,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I believe they must have felt the same thing when drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.07,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It hurts~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.70,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Always doing the facial expressions...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:58.50,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really, somehow, this is something I've always thought up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:04.26,chiwa,,0,0,0,,As a person who worked on this {\i1}Madoka{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs70}☆{\fn\fs}Magika{\i0}... it's really a work that everyone made, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:03.55,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.72,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I've had this conversation with Ao-chan a number of times, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:11.43,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's why, especially true for my acting of Homura, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:14.14,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"We entrust it to you," was said many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:19.94,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Little by little, stuff like how the tone of voice should be, or what is said where,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:27.78,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs50}鶴岡陽太{\fn\fs}(Tsuruoka Yota) = Sound Director
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.77,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I'd discuss that with Tsuruoka-san and would influence as much as I possibly could.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.99,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It was like that. All the way up until the final moments..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:30.07,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then when she becomes a little bit more {\i1}dere{\i0}, and perhaps before then, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:35.20,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It was like "As for facial expressions, this time they're being entrusted to you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.20,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.20,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It was something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:41.75,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's right, um, Homura—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.75,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Lots was left to each person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:47.63,taniguti,,0,0,0,,In relation to Homura, at this point she doesn't have that many facial expressions yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.63,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:48.76,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.39,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, but, it's in this episode, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.93,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, in just a little bit, that'll be there. It'll come, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.97,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It comes. "That" does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:58.85,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Well, QB is pretty simple, I think. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:06:59.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, ah, ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:06.15,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Um, I'd say this person's face doesn't change much. You can't tell what it's thinking, but it's a living thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.69,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,This feeling is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.28,taniguti,,0,0,0,,He just moves his tail around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.28,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:12.49,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,He moves it around like this, a cute little nyan-nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.49,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.03,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Irritates me. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.24,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:15.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:16.33,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then this face close-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That face close-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:17.95,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.79,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:23.79,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,When he moves his tail around like this, is he actually trying to convey something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:29.72,taniguti,,0,0,0,,No, not at all. Actually, that probably comes down to the people who draw or decide on the art for those cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:27.67,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.22,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Heee~ Ah, is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:34.35,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But, right now when he says "That is interesting" and such while moving his tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:34.35,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,it's like "I wonder if it moves when tension gets a bit higher."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:43.85,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,See, for cats, it's true for my own cat too, when they're irritated they'll "bang bang bang" their tails and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.39,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.52,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:47.94,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,or when they're like "I wonder what to do," their tail will go "fuyo!" up and such. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:51.20,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I was thinking, "Amazing, they took that sort of thing into account too," or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.78,chiwa,,0,0,0,,You know, for me, this kind of eye close-up is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.91,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne~?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:55.12,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.16,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Then, the editing has this sort of tawny feel to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.08,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.08,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:04.75,taniguti,,0,0,0,,When we first began this work, we had quite a few ideas which looked different. [more CG-ish, probably]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:11.05,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's different now. By now there are a lot of things that have a more "drawn" feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:09.42,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:16.60,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Those kind of touches were inserted by Kishida-san, the character designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:21.43,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, for things you'd say are in a hand-drawn style... Well, it's true here too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.44,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, the art has a feeling of being sketchy, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:23.44,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.52,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:23.73,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.90,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's another point of warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.36,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It has a bit of a "sepia" feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.61,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It has that kind of feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:29.61,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:35.57,taniguti,,0,0,0,,For that area, we asked staff of other works; it was rather difficult to obtain a unity throughout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.57,0:08:37.12,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:36.74,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.24,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Is that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:38.91,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:38.91,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:44.25,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Depending on what episode you're overseeing, how you view who the characters are will vary greatly, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:44.25,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.21,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's right, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.50,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it's true for their standpoints and such as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.50,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:51.88,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So in that case, facial expressions also really differ between episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:55.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,If people who drew for episode 1 saw an episode around this part,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.43,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"Eh!? What's this? They're totally different people!" is what they would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.64,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's to such an extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.64,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Things would be different~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.64,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The shape changes, doesn't it? Of this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.64,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:05.10,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think for that area, keeping balance must be incredibly troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:05.69,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:06.10,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:10.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But, um, especially for people who draw, umm, an episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:14.45,chiwa,,0,0,0,,For example, working on ep1, then afterward, something like ep5...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.62,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It must feel disjointed, right? Without seeing all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.62,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's right. Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:24.71,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So, do you have to explain things regarding that, such as "This is done in this manner" or "The world has become like this"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:27.46,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Well, that is a producer's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.54,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:31.88,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like Miyamoto-san, the Series Director's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.30,taniguti,,0,0,0,,He'd do that instead, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:40.55,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Taniguchi-san, do you look at the overall flow of conversations and say, "Don't do this kind of expression now,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:46.27,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"Do this with a more sorrowful feeling," or "Make this less sorrowful"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.27,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:34.67,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:47.73,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Do you strive to reach that kind of balance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:54.36,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's right, um, deciding on various things regarding CG or facial expressions of cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.03,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ohhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heee{\i0}~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.41,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But those are also trial cuts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.91,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I mean, for speech—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.49,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Well, one by one they become different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:00.49,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:06.83,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think this for our acting too, but what words were written, or how to say them, completely changed, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:09.75,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Being able to piece all of that together from those "trials" requires an amazing sense of balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.63,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne? It's amazing, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:15.46,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Really, the facial expressions have become completely different compared to my first time seeing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Hee~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.09,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:19.34,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, kind of... (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.18,chiwa,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of characters, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.18,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.35,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Who was the hardest person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.35,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:23.72,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.93,0:10:25.02,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That piques my interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:26.14,taniguti,,0,0,0,,The hardest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.98,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.94,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Oh~ Eh, so it's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.65,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Her eyelashes are big (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.40,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.32,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:40.24,taniguti,,0,0,0,,As far as drawing goes, she completely changes – the person who changes the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.74,taniguti,,0,0,0,,The character with the largest rate of change there. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:47.41,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Obtaining uniformity for that area was a little difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:46.83,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:47.41,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.46,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, conversely, easier characters to draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.29,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ah, eh... Homura, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.17,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:52.63,taniguti,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:54.21,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Oh, why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.59,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Nah, somehow... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:11:01.14,taniguti,,0,0,0,,A cool character has a lot of outside influence which help decide how to draw facial expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:03.72,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, I was told "We'll leave it to you" often.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.89,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:04.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:11.35,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really, for such a cool character, or a character that you believe doesn't get shaken up very much,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:15.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"There will be a lot of facial expressions" is something I really thought for Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.69,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ao-chan, you've said that too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:23.78,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, somehow, in episode one when Madoka is in disarray... she's actually in disarray and has a squeakiness to her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.99,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I think that is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:31.29,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It has this kind of design, but you can still do those expressions, amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.54,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:36.55,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Regarding the people who draw, there are a lot of them who like to draw cool facial expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.05,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.05,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}Ah{\alpha} I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.72,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Parts like those gloomy eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:47.81,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, but, certainly... especially for Homura-chan, whatever she does is always cool. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.56,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.81,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, those angles when she's agitated are quite scary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.31,taniguti,,0,0,0,,And then, when she turns around, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:54.65,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:57.69,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Since her hair is so long, it turns into such an intense drawing! Like right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.48,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:03.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah! Finally, right here... in front of someone else, she said "Madoka."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.91,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right—Right! That's right, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:08.74,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This episode left a huge impression on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:12.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,There's a lot that happens in conversation too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:16.59,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Homura, up until now, has kept how shaken up she is a secret inside of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.30,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Finally - SHE GETS TOTALLY SHAKEN UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:18.67,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Other people see it, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.34,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Totally shaken up~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:29.14,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I mean, there's the part coming up where the feelings she holds regarding Madoka finally come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.77,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Well, her feelings begin to be more at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.48,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.56,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Gradually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:42.82,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I, um, personally... well, coming this far, Ao-chan and I like Kyouko-tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:48.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,How is it to draw a straightforward girl such as Kyouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:52.00,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Right, well, Kyouko is another character who was easy to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.00,taniguti,,0,0,0,,She's somewhat of a standard character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.92,chiwa,,0,0,0,,There's a direct connection, right? Between her feelings and facial expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.00,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:58.50,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.04,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.42,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Kyouko~{\fnArial Unicode MS}♥{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:02.72,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Kyouko, you know, when she comes, it's very calming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.05,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Kyouko, so relieving, Kyouko~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.89,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah... ha~{\fnArial Unicode MS}♥{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:11.64,taniguti,,0,0,0,,She's the character who'll mostly appear at any place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.31,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.81,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She's human, isn't she? Extremely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:19.52,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,The fact that she thinks humans can be good,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.11,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,that part of Kyouko-tan is relieving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:24.11,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I love what happens right after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.95,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This "Khan!" thing she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.78,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right? This, ne~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.87,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think it's very girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.87,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:29.58,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Actually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.95,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, um, sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This very "real" topic begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:33.62,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.50,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Super extravagant hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.50,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Super extravagant hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It really drives me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.04,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,AHHHHHHhhhhhhh! (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.05,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"With pleasure" they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.05,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's "With pleasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:42.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.17,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS}كا كا شى أماه دي ما{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:48.97,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, um... Miki Shinchirou-san and Tobita-san are both amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:58.15,notes,,0,0,0,,Miki Shinchirou-san and Tobita [Nobuo]-san are the voice actors for these hosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:49.55,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.51,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.47,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:58.15,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Tsuruoka-san went this far to put his hand into this work, it really moves me. I've said to Tsuruoka-san:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.61,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"Tsuruoka-san has such fighting spirit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:07.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Calling in these two to play the roles of these hosts... I think it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:07.99,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.57,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right, right, I really think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.57,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ne~?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:14.37,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But somehow, since I didn't think that would be the case, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:18.75,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,When I saw the cast list, it was like "Mm?" ... "Mm!?" (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:22.63,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, it's quite tight-knit, isn't it? The workplace had a very tight-knit feeling to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.55,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:29.89,chiwa,,0,0,0,,In the workplace there are a lot of girls, so overall everyone understands [each other]...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.22,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.43,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:32.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So it was really very tightly knit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, at the workplace where you draw scenes, that kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:40.56,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Does the atmosphere and such change because of the members?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:45.98,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... Well, actually, work from home is pretty common. Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.23,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's piques my interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:44.94,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:45.65,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:50.78,taniguti,,0,0,0,,So, you have your own kind of nature around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:51.12,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:56.75,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Not working with other people very often... isn't very unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.41,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have that feeling at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.16,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:58.75,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:14:59.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.92,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Well, especially in this work, the manual labor parts [are done at home].
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.88,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:04.96,taniguti,,0,0,0,,For times like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.96,chiwa,,0,0,0,,You have to gradually track the people down, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.05,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That would certainly be true for the current {\i1}sekaikan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.68,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,"No! No! I don't want to come out!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:12.34,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.64,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But, the atmosphere at the actual workplace is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.31,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.35,taniguti,,0,0,0,,I'd have to say there's a lot of guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.48,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ehhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I feel like guys draw girls cuter than girls do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.57,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:25.57,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:28.32,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,They're surely able to recognize the cute parts of girls, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.45,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,They really get that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.49,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:37.79,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Really, starting from this point, he really sticks to his agenda...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.87,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs100}ヽ(`Д´)ﾉ{\fn\fs} Q—BUAIIIIIIIII~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:44.04,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, just like this, there's a lot of scenes where they just stop, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.67,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Where a character or situation stops, and they just think for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:50.01,chiwa,,0,0,0,,For times like this, are you cautious about...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:54.80,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Well, I always think "Ah, the visuals are moving about," like different objects are moving, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:59.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Do you put a lot of thought into balance for those "other items" on screen too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:04.69,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Right, that is lumped together in content, with CG.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.90,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.44,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Well, if everything just stopped, that'd be weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.90,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:15.53,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then, for example, right now this water fountain - the color keeps shifting about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:21.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow doesn't that display her - Madoka's - emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.41,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.08,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Right, right. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.25,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think that this is just such a complete work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.17,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne~?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.09,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I can really feel that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:33.55,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mm, somehow, for us there is a lot to think about, since we hear a lot of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:38.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,We think about many things with a "doing the drama ourselves"-style feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:45.02,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This art of drama is truly amazing, I feel very fortunate for being able to do this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:45.77,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:46.86,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:54.49,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So just like here... When humans think of or say things, how will they move after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.78,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It makes you think about every day observations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:57.49,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.20,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:05.04,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Well, we wanted you to observe things unintentionally in this scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.25,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ah, but we might see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:06.96,taniguti,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.88,chiwa,,0,0,0,,That's right, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:07.88,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord1.8}(Ah, shaki)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.04,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona}(｀・ω・´) ｼｬｷｰﾝ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.04,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona}(｀・ω・´) ｼｬｷｰﾝ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.59,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Suddenly shakiin (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:16.13,notes,,0,0,0,,{\fnMona}(｀・ω・´) ｼｬｷｰﾝ{\fn} (Shakiin)\NThis is a term / emote that is used when tension is rising.\NI cannot give you the origin or a literal TL of "Shakiin" itself, as I do not know it. It seems that it may have originated from a Japanese TV show of the same name, or it's just a sound effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:15.26,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Really, when it comes time to draw the drama, you can't read too much of it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.51,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:21.93,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Then, those who feel it stronger are the animators... as they are able to watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:22.77,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.27,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ahh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:26.44,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,I see. That's right, everyone is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.06,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.57,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Not just humans, but even this type of animal-thing, they're able to depict it well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.57,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.36,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.11,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:34.53,others,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnMona\fs110}＼{\fnArial Unicode MS\fs150}GOOD SHOT!{\fnMona\fs110}／
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.44,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Yup it's come~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:38.41,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Tonight, she'll do a little bit of an attack, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.41,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,The lights have become red. (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.32,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.03,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:44.66,chiwa,,0,0,0,,You know, the Homura right here, I really love her~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:48.38,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,And Madoka's surprised face she's making here is also amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.29,chiwa,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1.2}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.00,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol) I'm looking at QB.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.00,taniguti,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:55.38,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Despite that, Madoka can just stay sitting there. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.38,taniguti,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:59.18,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right here she finally really explodes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.14,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:17:59.72,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.85,chiwa,,0,0,0,,She does, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:06.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I hadn't done any crying up until now, so I was very surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:12.11,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But, what is it, when acting as her, my voice just wouldn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.32,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.32,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:13.86,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:18.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Somehow, ne... her emotions are too heavy. If this were real, it'd be like:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:22.12,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"WHAT DO I DO!?" is the kind of feeling it'd have, since it hurts so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.70,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then she loses all of her strength, and is unable to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:26.62,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:32.79,chiwa,,0,0,0,,For acting out this girl—It was even properly written in the script,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:38.55,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"There might be people out there that think this is because she's run out of power, but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,"That isn't the case, instead she's this type of girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:45.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,she tries and tries, then goes "Waaah!", then "Ahhh," and loses her strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.14,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:52.31,chiwa,,0,0,0,,When she loses her footing, the girl's weak parts come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.82,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This scene left a very large impression on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.69,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mm. Now, she says her name for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.24,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:58.78,taniguti,,0,0,0,,She shouts it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:58.95,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.99,chiwa,,0,0,0,,But you know, somehow, it's like it reaches her yet it doesn't reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:07.29,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Then she screams out "MADOKAAAAAA!" when normally she wouldn't call that out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.49,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:08.37,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:08.87,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This girl's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:12.25,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I love the facial expression right after this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.96,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This you know, who was it, I wonder, during interviews...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:21.39,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I'm asked, "Since expression doesn't change too much, does Madoka have drama?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.10,chiwa,,0,0,0,,I think, "No, no, no."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:28.35,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The biggest enemy in front of them, is the sudden "fate of a girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.35,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&}Tdhe biggest enemy in front of them, is the sudden {\alpha}fate{\alpha&HFF&} of a girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.60,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think it was properly done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.73,chiwa,,0,0,0,,This strength of a girl. And, this sort of general expectation—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.40,taniguti,,0,0,0,,(lol) This.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.48,chiwa,,0,0,0,,(lol) This guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.24,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Frustrating me! (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.57,chiwa,,0,0,0,,The way this guy moves (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.36,taniguti,,0,0,0,,(lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:44.78,chiwa,,0,0,0,,So, the fact that even though this was written by guy[s], I thought it was able to achieve such portrayal of girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.74,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne~?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:45.41,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Ne? That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:45.62,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.16,chiwa,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.70,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It has a lot of that, doesn't it, Ao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:50.37,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,It's there. It's definitely there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:53.67,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,That's right, somehow, Homura-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:54.96,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:59.38,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,She's constantly straining and straining, and even though at first she kept her distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:02.63,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,But when Madoka's confidence is lacking just a little bit—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:07.22,chiwa,,0,0,0,,It's not yet different; In this world, it's still impossible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:04.34,ao-chan,,0,0,0,,Right–Right.
