Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:48.72,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Mm, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:54.56,taniguti,,0,0,0,,Well, personally, I've done {\i1}mahou shoujo{\i0} things in the past, but...
