Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:58.56,taniguti,,0,0,0,,But this one has a completely different point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:01.77,taniguti,,0,0,0,,And it became a work with such a huge headquarters.
